Rowdy Wolf:




In the distance, he saw Predacons before a large ship, a spider, a 
frog and another. (Tarantulas, Paralysis and Hell Beast) From his 
observations, and a little guessing, they were from the faction 
Quickstrike belonged to. He had to be apart of the Vok. He was chosen.

He howled to let the trio know that he was there.
